                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature touches the manacles</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The spirit attempts to lock the manacles around the triggering creature's wrists. The triggering creature must attempt a @Check[type:reflex|dc:23] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The spirit loosely places manacles around the creature's wrists. Removing the manacles requires a single action.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The spirit clamps the manacles around the creature's wrists but fails to lock them. The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} until the manacles are removed as a 3-action activity.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The spirit clamps the manacles around the creature's wrists and locks them. The creature is flat-footed and clumsy 1 until the manacles are removed (@Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Escape]{Escape} DC 23, simple lock).</p>"
